Unity Catalog is an open source storage layer which is used to classify and manage data

It helps us in keeping track of multiple workspace and multiple teams data inside a single
place.

It provide security features such as permission where we can grant permission to specific
users for specific access such as read ,write or update.

Inside DataBricks we have one option called Unity Catalogue we have to click on it
then we have a option called add Data then we have to click on create a Catalogue.

